      • doCQL2MetasearchCommand

        public String doCQL2MetasearchCommand(String cqlSearchQuery)
        Converts a CQL-formatted search query into a format that the Web2 Bridge can understand. Uses org.z3950.zing.cql.CQLNode.toXCQL() and SAX Parsing to convert the cqlSearchQuery into a find_command.
        Parameters:
        cqlSearchQuery - CQL-formatted search query.
        Returns:
        X-Server find_command or null if cqlSearchQuery is null or empty.
        See Also:
        org.z3950.zing.cql.CQLNode.toXCQL()
